FeedPackage.Tags: DI Dependency Injection IoC Inversion of Control Framework
FeedPackage.Title: IoC

FeedPackage.Description:
This is a IoC container based on Dependency Injection. As dependencies are controlled with attributes, you do not need any code to register, lookup, or wire object instances.
